unnormalised: JEE Main che results bhair aile! Ani are baba, Delhi railway station-acher chaai porosui chalu asa mhamnnatt memechyo dharo suru zaleat. 10 lakh vidhyarthi bhag ghetle, ani sangpak zai mhonnleear atancheak tor sab gulab jamun gheun utsav korun nam.
normalised: J-E-E Main results bhair aile! Ani are baba, Delhi railway station-acher chaye porosui vegim memes bhair poddtai. dha lakh vidhyarthi bosle, ani sangtat mhonnlear soglle gulab jamun khanun somrombhan kortole na.

unnormalised: Aikuunk melltta ki, IIT khatir cutoffs hea varsaak Mount Everest porosui unch dista. Mhonncheak, tum IIT Bombay-k Computer Science khatir taryari kortaa zalear, tumka nidrantui coding korchinn poddttoli. Sutranche mhonnea poros, 99.99 percentile mhonnlear navin average asa. Itlea velar, Sharma kakai bhair-ant tumchea putanche mark tumchea markanchea sangata tulna kortolo, to Sharmaji ka beta "America-nt settle zala" zalearui. Tea ulavnneantlean suttpak zai tor bhagya tumchem.
normalised: Sangtat mhonnlear, I-I-T khatir cutoffs hea vorosak Mount Everest porosui unch distat. Mhonnche I-I-T Bombay-nt Computer Science khatir tuvem sopnantui coding korun zai. Sources sangtat ninety nine point nine nine percentile mhonnche navo average. Ithlean Sharma mama-i tumchea markanchem tulon tacho put "America-nt settle zala" zaleari kortolo. Tea bhassen bolnaarponnachem dusrem kam korunk melonk na.

unnormalised: Kota-ntlean coaching center zalzalleat. Thoddea utsavachi tayyari pattlean ghevpaak bharti asa, ani thoddea "fuddlea varsak tor zaitich" mhonnchea vixrvaska divpak wat soddta. Counseling session Bollywood-antlea climax scene porosui khup bhari asa.
normalised: Kota-nt coaching centers bazu marun zatat. Kaim zat-fast somrombhan kortole, zalear kaim avoy-bapayank patieunk lagta "uchit voros mhonnche heach voros." counseling sessions Bollywood climax scene porosui zorachi asa.

unnormalised: Dusrea khobranche mhonnea poros, Guwahati-ntlea ek vidhyarthyane examiner-ak 500 rupeanchi lanch divpak yotn kelo. వివరాలు ఇనికాయ్ ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟ್ నాయి. పీనాత్ పన్ అమీకే శాస్త్రైనిగా జూగాతని లా స్కూల్-అక్తరు జొగ్ని. దిషోనైనకళావ్ డివోరి.
normalised: Dusre khobren, Guwahati-cho ek vidhyarthi invigilator-ak panch so rupayanchi lanch diunk sodlo. Details porimpuranen aile nat, punn kiteak mhonnche taka law school-an bhettoch mhonn mhanni. Apparently, vaait vellar vaait upay korche podta.

unnormalised: Private college aanandaan hat ghasunk toyar asat. IIT-ache sopan thoddeank dur bhitar zatach, hi mandirean (vanchuk: dharann bhari fees ghevun) vidhyarthyank ukti bhaan-n swagat korpak toyar asa. Chennai-ntl ek engineering college "jobachi zameenvari" scheme-ui divpak toyar asa – conditions lagu zatatuch, te dishtti asa.
normalised: Private colleges khuxal zata. I-I-T sopon khobren dusrea vorosak dhaklea urlear, hea institutions ukttea hatan vidhyarthyank "welcome" kortat (vaach "mothe fees ghetat"). Chennai-ntlea eke engineering college-n "guaranteed job placement" scheme-i dilya - nimnanaam niyama, thode dusren zatat.

unnormalised: Hea bhovtalleantle, cut-off-ache bhair marka melltoleank visronka nam. Te "azun kasheak" ani "jarur" hea ulavneache chokrache bhair poddak nam. Pan are baba, CAT, UPSC ani IAS officer zavpacho uchch marg asatuch. Bhavishya ujvalla asa, athamchea divsa zodd… dharann dabav asa.
normalised: Hea sogllea gombhiray-an, cutoff thode unne zalear vidhyarthyank dusrea vatten sanglem. Te "kiteak" ani "uchit" mhonnche ek loop-an addkleat. Punn are, thodak C-A-T, U-P-S-C, ani I-A-S officer zaun pavunk favo asa. Bhavitvy ujvalla asa, punn aachoch hall... stressfull asa.

unnormalised: Ani nimanneak, tumi yaad dovrat bhavaamno, mark tumchem mully sangnak nam! Tum IIT-ak apply kortat zalear soddun, tenna te sangtat. Thoddo jhok chalu asa (khareak thoddo). Counseling proccess-ak tumchen shubha aasa. Tumchen bhavishya tumche bhagyaani bhov asaav. Ani tumchea internet connection-ak 25/06/2024-acher seat melloupache ghainean suttka mellov!
normalised: Ani nimanne, lokaank yaad diunchem, marks tuka nirupyog korina! Kiteak mhonnche tum I-I-T khatir apply korunk bhair ailear, tannim kitem korunk favo. Mhanni khelli mhonnche (most). Counseling process-ak subhechha diunk favo! May the odds be ever in your favor. Ani tumchem internet connection seat allocation khatir rush mhonnche twenty fifth june two thousand and twenty four-ak urovunk favo.
